body:
Only tutorial that is yet to be ported is Q-learning. I've looked over this and I think we can port that too without leaving out much.

Only problem I foresee is documentation build environment creating a problem because of [this issue](https://github.com/openai/gym/issues/462) of openai gym. But then they suggest a solution in the issue anyways.

Edit: Q-learning tutorial added. All tutorials are now ported.
